WEBVTT

00:00:09.333 --> 00:00:11.417
[footsteps pattering]

00:00:11.458 --> 00:00:14.333
[CLARA] Whoosh, whoosh,
whoosh, rawr!

00:00:14.375 --> 00:00:16.583
[singsongy] Ooh, I want
someone to play with me.

00:00:16.625 --> 00:00:18.917
But who is that gonna be?

00:00:20.292 --> 00:00:21.750
[NARRATOR] The netherworld.

00:00:21.792 --> 00:00:24.583
The realm where all demons live.

00:00:24.625 --> 00:00:29.417
And the monarch who rules is,
the Demon King.

00:00:29.458 --> 00:00:31.750
However, the Demon King's throne

00:00:31.792 --> 00:00:33.833
has sat empty for ages.

00:00:37.250 --> 00:00:39.292
Only the most worthy
will inherit

00:00:39.333 --> 00:00:41.292
this seat of sovereignty,

00:00:41.333 --> 00:00:43.167
but who will it be?

00:02:18.750 --> 00:02:20.417
[IRUMA AND CLARA]
"Iruma and Clara."

00:02:22.458 --> 00:02:24.417
♪

00:02:24.458 --> 00:02:26.042
[CLARA yells in distance]

00:02:26.083 --> 00:02:27.125
-[IRUMA] Huh?
-Wait.

00:02:27.167 --> 00:02:28.167
There's something
going on in there.

00:02:28.208 --> 00:02:30.000
-[thudding]
-[muffled screeching]

00:02:30.042 --> 00:02:32.667
[CLARA] Rolling. Rolling!

00:02:32.708 --> 00:02:34.958
[IRUMA] Huh? [gasps]

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:36.750
Um, are you okay?

00:02:36.792 --> 00:02:38.375
Strike!

00:02:38.417 --> 00:02:40.625
[laughs]

00:02:40.667 --> 00:02:41.917
I'm Clara.

00:02:41.958 --> 00:02:43.917
My right foot's Connor
and my left foot's Murf.

00:02:43.958 --> 00:02:46.167
I have a familiar
that's named Falfal.

00:02:46.208 --> 00:02:47.833
You wouldn't wanna eat
some candy, would ya?

00:02:47.875 --> 00:02:50.167
When you see a big pile of stuff
in front of you,

00:02:50.208 --> 00:02:51.875
don't you just wanna go kaboom?

00:02:51.917 --> 00:02:53.917
Ooh, I'm gonna do it again,
just watch me.

00:02:53.958 --> 00:02:55.333
It's gonna be great.

00:02:55.375 --> 00:02:57.208
♪ If it's for Daddy ♪

00:02:57.250 --> 00:02:59.250
♪ I'll skip to my Lou ♪

00:02:59.292 --> 00:03:01.208
♪ And if it's for my Mommy ♪

00:03:01.250 --> 00:03:03.708
♪ I'll pat-a-cake
and pat-a-cake ♪

00:03:03.750 --> 00:03:05.583
Stop stacking those boxes now.

00:03:05.625 --> 00:03:07.667
--[CLARA] ♪ I'll skip to my Lou ♪
--Clara Valac.

00:03:07.708 --> 00:03:10.125
She's famous
for being a colossal weirdo.

00:03:10.167 --> 00:03:13.000
She can be majorly clingy,
so people avoid her.

00:03:13.042 --> 00:03:15.417
-[IRUMA] They do?
-I said, stop it immediately!

00:03:15.458 --> 00:03:16.542
...a single one!

00:03:16.583 --> 00:03:17.500
You're Iruma.

00:03:17.542 --> 00:03:19.292
And you must be Asmodeus, right?

00:03:19.333 --> 00:03:21.542
Iruma and Asmodeus?

00:03:21.583 --> 00:03:23.333
You can handle this.

00:03:24.583 --> 00:03:25.458
[BOTH gasp]

00:03:25.500 --> 00:03:27.000
[laughs]

00:03:28.750 --> 00:03:29.833
[IRUMA yells]

00:03:29.875 --> 00:03:30.917
Off you go.

00:03:30.958 --> 00:03:32.208
[CLARA] Whoa!

00:03:32.250 --> 00:03:34.708
Oh, dear, you forgot
your textbooks.

00:03:34.750 --> 00:03:37.792
[ASMODEUS] Iruma, sir.
Are you alright, master?

00:03:37.833 --> 00:03:41.167
-[laughing]
-[IRUMA chuckles]

00:03:41.208 --> 00:03:43.708
Iruma-kins. Azz-Azz.
What do you wanna play?

00:03:43.750 --> 00:03:45.708
-Iruma-kins?
-Uh, Azz-Azz?

00:03:45.750 --> 00:03:47.333
I've got tons of things.

00:03:47.375 --> 00:03:49.583
A spiky ball. A nom-nom book.

00:03:49.625 --> 00:03:52.792
A broken, bloody,
family murder house set.

00:03:52.833 --> 00:03:53.875
[ASMODEUS] We should flee.

00:03:53.917 --> 00:03:55.000
Huh? Oh, but...

00:03:55.042 --> 00:03:56.375
[CLARA] Let's play murder house.

00:03:56.417 --> 00:03:58.000
Iruma-kins, would you please be

00:03:58.042 --> 00:03:59.542
the tree in our yard?

00:03:59.583 --> 00:04:01.000
[IRUMA] "Please"?

00:04:01.042 --> 00:04:05.000
[CLARA]
Please. Please. Please. Please.

00:04:05.042 --> 00:04:06.667
[grunts sharply]

00:04:06.708 --> 00:04:09.542
[NARRATOR] Iruma can't decline
a single request from anyone.

00:04:09.583 --> 00:04:12.125
Remember, he's a total pushover.

00:04:12.167 --> 00:04:15.167
Beautiful tree.

00:04:15.208 --> 00:04:16.417
[ASMODEUS] Master, don't!

00:04:16.458 --> 00:04:17.708
Now, would you pretend

00:04:17.750 --> 00:04:19.667
you're a really strong wind,
pretty please?

00:04:19.708 --> 00:04:20.667
[grunts sharply]

00:04:20.708 --> 00:04:22.250
Please. Please.

00:04:22.292 --> 00:04:24.042
Please. Please.

00:04:24.083 --> 00:04:26.583
Nice wind, ohh!

00:04:26.625 --> 00:04:28.125
[IRUMA] Ooh-whee! [chuckling]

00:04:28.167 --> 00:04:29.208
[ASMODEUS] Please stop it!

00:04:29.250 --> 00:04:31.542
Now pretend to be
my pet demon dog,

00:04:31.583 --> 00:04:32.750
if you'd please.

00:04:32.792 --> 00:04:34.875
-[grunts sharply]
-Please. Please. Please.

00:04:34.917 --> 00:04:37.000
Please. Please. Please.

00:04:37.042 --> 00:04:38.375
[IRUMA barks, pants]

00:04:38.417 --> 00:04:39.792
Good boy.

00:04:39.833 --> 00:04:41.750
[ASMODEUS] Iruma, sir!

00:04:41.792 --> 00:04:44.042
Azz-Azz, you'll be
the young housewife next door

00:04:44.083 --> 00:04:46.000
that my husband
cheats on me with.

00:04:46.042 --> 00:04:47.833
This is unacceptable!

00:04:47.875 --> 00:04:50.250
How dare you make
Master Iruma a pet?

00:04:50.292 --> 00:04:51.625
Let's play, Azz-Azz.

00:04:51.667 --> 00:04:52.500
[gasps]

00:04:54.458 --> 00:04:56.542
[ASMODEUS] Will you hurry up
and divorce him?

00:04:56.583 --> 00:04:58.417
You are the worst wife ever!

00:04:58.458 --> 00:05:00.125
I'm abandoning
the much older husband

00:05:00.167 --> 00:05:01.208
I was forced to marry,

00:05:01.250 --> 00:05:02.583
then I'll show your husband

00:05:02.625 --> 00:05:04.250
some much needed euphoric bliss!

00:05:04.292 --> 00:05:06.708
You're so gifted.
What a natural.

00:05:06.750 --> 00:05:07.792
[CLARA] Hyah!

00:05:07.833 --> 00:05:09.042
[ASMODEUS screams]

00:05:09.083 --> 00:05:10.333
-Yay!
-Are you out of your mind?!

00:05:10.375 --> 00:05:12.417
Stop this bloodbath
of a lovers' quarrel.

00:05:12.458 --> 00:05:14.625
Huh? How is the dog
supposed to do that?

00:05:14.667 --> 00:05:17.500
[laughing]

00:05:17.542 --> 00:05:19.958
We need someone to be
the husband and cat.

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:21.583
[CLARA]
Connor and Murf can play them.

00:05:21.625 --> 00:05:22.875
Here you go.

00:05:22.917 --> 00:05:24.417
But, first, say hi.

00:05:24.458 --> 00:05:27.708
Uh, how do you do? Ugh.

00:05:27.750 --> 00:05:29.208
Azz-Azz, the husband's here.

00:05:29.250 --> 00:05:31.167
Ooh, think of the secrets.

00:05:31.208 --> 00:05:32.708
[CLARA giggles]

00:05:32.750 --> 00:05:35.708
Now, now, young wife next door
cheating with my husband,

00:05:35.750 --> 00:05:36.958
and you too, doggy.

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:38.208
You're done for the day.

00:05:39.708 --> 00:05:41.208
Giddyap. Hyah.

00:05:41.250 --> 00:05:43.708
-[laughs]
-You okay down there?

00:05:43.750 --> 00:05:45.125
Perfectly fine!

00:05:45.167 --> 00:05:46.875
Yay! Yay!

00:05:46.917 --> 00:05:48.250
You're gonna regret this, Valac.

00:05:48.292 --> 00:05:49.125
[laughing]

00:05:49.167 --> 00:05:51.583
[IRUMA] Huh? [chuckles]

00:05:51.625 --> 00:05:53.583
[screaming]

00:05:53.625 --> 00:05:54.958
[CLARA laughing]

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:57.750
[ASMODEUS] Come on! Oh, no!

00:05:57.792 --> 00:06:00.167
[IRUMA panting]

00:06:00.208 --> 00:06:01.708
[gasps] Huh?

00:06:08.875 --> 00:06:10.125
[IRUMA gasps]

00:06:10.167 --> 00:06:11.542
[IRUMA]
I wonder what's in there.

00:06:11.583 --> 00:06:12.667
[wind gusting]

00:06:15.250 --> 00:06:17.333
[laughs] Goal!

00:06:18.917 --> 00:06:20.042
-Oh, please.
-[ASMODEUS panting]

00:06:20.083 --> 00:06:22.083
Clara, I just can't.

00:06:22.125 --> 00:06:23.542
Two hours nonstop.

00:06:23.583 --> 00:06:24.958
-[IRUMA groans]
[panting continues]

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:27.458
Hey. Up. Come on.

00:06:30.667 --> 00:06:34.042
Here. I have snacks, too.

00:06:34.083 --> 00:06:35.500
Oh, thanks a lot.

00:06:35.542 --> 00:06:37.000
What is that?

00:06:37.042 --> 00:06:39.125
[CLARA]
They're my family's specialty.

00:06:40.583 --> 00:06:42.000
[SNAKE] Hiss, hiss...

00:06:42.042 --> 00:06:44.667
I can make just about anything
I've seen before appear.

00:06:44.708 --> 00:06:46.042
[IRUMA] Really? Cool.

00:06:46.083 --> 00:06:48.042
Hey, Clarin. What's up?

00:06:48.083 --> 00:06:50.042
[chuckles] Yocchin.

00:06:50.083 --> 00:06:53.500
[YOCCHAN] Well, well, did you
acquire some more owners?

00:06:53.542 --> 00:06:55.708
Uh-huh. [chuckles]

00:06:55.750 --> 00:06:57.125
[IRUMA] Owners?

00:06:57.167 --> 00:06:59.250
Whatever. Make with the drinks.

00:06:59.292 --> 00:07:00.375
[giggles]

00:07:02.833 --> 00:07:03.792
Here.

00:07:04.792 --> 00:07:06.000
Thank you much.

00:07:06.042 --> 00:07:07.500
-[BOTH laugh]
-Later.

00:07:07.542 --> 00:07:08.875
-[BOYS] Later.
-[CLARA] Buh-bye!

00:07:10.958 --> 00:07:12.708
Who were those guys?

00:07:12.750 --> 00:07:15.583
Well, see,
when I do favors for them,

00:07:15.625 --> 00:07:16.875
it makes them happy,

00:07:16.917 --> 00:07:18.875
and then they
sometimes play with me.

00:07:18.917 --> 00:07:22.000
Clarin, mind giving us
some snacks?

00:07:22.042 --> 00:07:22.875
Sure.

00:07:25.167 --> 00:07:26.125
Here.

00:07:26.167 --> 00:07:27.375
[YOCCHAN] Rock on.

00:07:27.417 --> 00:07:29.583
Okay, ready? Fetch!

00:07:29.625 --> 00:07:31.125
[CLARA]
Woof. Woof, woof, woof, woof.

00:07:31.167 --> 00:07:33.083
[laughing]

00:07:34.292 --> 00:07:35.583
[YOCCHAN] We want popsicles.

00:07:38.125 --> 00:07:39.292
Thanks a mil.

00:07:39.333 --> 00:07:42.208
Time for hide-and-seek.
You're it, Clarin.

00:07:42.250 --> 00:07:43.583
Count to 50,000.

00:07:43.625 --> 00:07:47.792
-[CLARA] One, two, three...
-[BOYS laughing]

00:07:47.833 --> 00:07:52.583
...20,159, 20,160, 20,161.

00:07:52.625 --> 00:07:58.833
20,162, 20,163, 20,164.

00:07:58.875 --> 00:08:00.083
That seems kinda...

00:08:00.125 --> 00:08:01.958
[CLARA]
Oh, no. Don't you get it?

00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:04.875
You two are the first ones
to actually play with me.

00:08:04.917 --> 00:08:08.250
Anyway, so, uh...

00:08:08.292 --> 00:08:11.583
Will you maybe
play with me again?

00:08:11.625 --> 00:08:12.667
Sure.

00:08:13.792 --> 00:08:15.417
[squeals in excitement]

00:08:16.750 --> 00:08:20.417
Please, let's not, master.
We might catch her crazy.

00:08:20.458 --> 00:08:22.708
Azz-Azz, you're alive again.
Wanna play with us?

00:08:22.750 --> 00:08:24.833
Let's run a hellish demonathon.
You ready?

00:08:24.875 --> 00:08:27.208
[IRUMA] Um, maybe it's best
we stop for the day?

00:08:27.250 --> 00:08:29.708
[rooster crows]

00:08:29.750 --> 00:08:32.208
-[cacophonous screeching]
-[IRUMA screams]

00:08:32.250 --> 00:08:34.583
That thing's
gonna give me a heart attack!

00:08:37.833 --> 00:08:39.625
See you later.

00:08:39.667 --> 00:08:40.583
Bye, pumpkin.

00:08:40.625 --> 00:08:43.167
Have a good day!

00:08:43.208 --> 00:08:46.167
It would appear he's adjusting
to the school nicely.

00:08:46.208 --> 00:08:48.042
[chuckles] Yes.

00:08:48.083 --> 00:08:50.833
He's growing up so fast,
I'm just filled with joy.

00:08:50.875 --> 00:08:52.167
[OPERA] Hmm.

00:08:53.708 --> 00:08:56.167
[CLARA laughs] So high!

00:08:56.208 --> 00:08:57.167
[IRUMA] Huh?

00:08:57.208 --> 00:08:58.208
-[CLARA] Huh?
-[ASMODEUS] Hmm?

00:08:58.250 --> 00:09:00.042
-[gasps, chuckles]
-[gasps]

00:09:00.083 --> 00:09:01.167
No peeking!

00:09:01.208 --> 00:09:03.458
Don't be shy, Azz-Azz.

00:09:03.500 --> 00:09:05.167
What are you talking about?

00:09:05.208 --> 00:09:06.458
-Stop that.
-[CLARA] It's okay.

00:09:06.500 --> 00:09:07.500
-[ASMODEUS] No, it's not.
-[CLARA] It's okay.

00:09:07.542 --> 00:09:08.417
[ASMODEUS] I said, no, it's not.

00:09:08.458 --> 00:09:09.292
[CLARA] It's okay.

00:09:09.333 --> 00:09:10.167
[ASMODEUS] Get off!

00:09:11.708 --> 00:09:14.542
Okay. One for you,
and one for you.

00:09:14.583 --> 00:09:15.958
-[ASMODEUS] Hmm.
-[IRUMA] Uh...

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:18.042
-Uh, thank you.
-[gulping]

00:09:20.042 --> 00:09:21.250
Hmm.

00:09:24.708 --> 00:09:26.750
[CLARA] ♪ I'm a lucky girl ♪

00:09:26.792 --> 00:09:29.167
♪ We'll have all the fun
in the world ♪

00:09:29.208 --> 00:09:31.792
[scatting]

00:09:31.833 --> 00:09:34.167
[BOY 1] That honor student
sure likes weirdos.

00:09:34.208 --> 00:09:36.417
I mean, he's still
hanging out with her.

